Given a year, find whether leap year or not?

Input Description:
Given a 4 digit number

Output Description:
Print leap year or not a leap year

Sample Input :
1996
Sample Output :
leap year

      n = int(input())
      if n % 400 == 0 and n % 100 == 0 or n % 4 == 0:
          print("leap year")
      else:
          print("not a leap year")
